Flicker/Phoenix/Skyblaze::

"Perhaps," Skyblaze agrees, rather unemotionally.  He literally 
floats down the corridor after the other two.  "Let's go."

Flicker gets outside and confronts Aerotaur.  "So we meet again.  I 
hope you're not still trying to get me to rethink my actions - it 
won't work."

Phoenix stays behind the acting-commander of the Predacons, a little 
shy about this newcomer.
